Placeholder so the audits/ folder exists in the repo even before the
first comment-audit receipt is authored.

Per `.github/playbooks/comment-protocol.md` §Persisted audit record:
in this instructions repo each commit authors `last.md` here (gitignored,
overwritten per commit); the post-commit hook flushes it into a LOCAL git
note and deletes it. Nothing in audits/ except this placeholder is tracked.
